        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Used to add sub-maps of the obsidian vault, meaning a specific subfolder that's synced when the rest of the vault isn't. This is only enabled and only takes effect when the full vault sync setting is disabled.",
