        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "If set, the plugin will only tell you what it would've done, but not actually do it. Meaning tell you which files it would change, but not actually do the changes. Useful for debugging, or just making sure you trust the plugin",
